{"tid":1692033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喺香港搞大型罷工係好難，但並非冇可能","createTime":"2019-11-04T02:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T12:13:16.000Z","uid":240250,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f5bb1426871f871dd4eebe96fbce6c4d3c98781c","tid":1692033,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:01:02.000Z","msg":"困難：<br />\n<br />\n1. 公會冇用，香港地嚴重向資方好多年，畀你短期內成立到個工會都冇牙力。<br />\n<br />\n2. 基金冇用，罷工等於辭職，你基金幫得一時幫唔得一世，再者可能有人好鍾意原本份工，轉工搵工又係麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n3. 私人公司罷工冇用，細公司罷工只係表態，你唔賺錢你既事，政府wfc。<br />\n<br />\n4. 最重要既一點，就係香港人仲過到正常生活。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我見好多人討論緊工會同基金，但我覺得應該由第四點開始著手，令香港人過唔返正常生活先。"},{"pid":"1387186b2431944bd8523a8c215f2ebb8380637c","tid":1692033,"uid":170297,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:11:54.000Z","msg":"值得討論下"},{"pid":"4878ea7b643516d9d1a7c31346c150858c5fa9af","tid":1692033,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1387186b2431944bd8523a8c215f2ebb8380637c","tid":1692033,"uid":170297,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:11:54.000Z","msg":"值得討論下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:23:37.000Z","msg":"解決唔到第四點既話，就算滿足到頭兩點都冇用，因為香港人一定係求安穩"},{"pid":"07e143baa2d52ab7b1486b7eda6d3b4e1beb71fb","tid":1692033,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f812c4d938f0e6b711c0a0300cf91a6e342288","tid":1692033,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07e143baa2d52ab7b1486b7eda6d3b4e1beb71fb","tid":1692033,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e5150ed5082f67582485635627dfca16d49681","tid":1692033,"uid":57424,"like":1,"di